OL,3,CInternational cricket umpire Michael
OL,4,CGough refuses breath test after night
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FLeading cricket umpire Michael Gough
OL,8,Fhas been banned from driving and fined
OL,9,Fmore than #4,000 after refusing to
OL,10,Fprovide a breath sample to police.
OL,12,FOfficers had attended his home in
OL,13,FHartlepool on 1 August after he
OL,14,Freturned from a night out in Durham
OL,15,Fwith his partner.
OL,17,FThe 44-year-old claims he had a vodka
OL,18,Fafter arriving back at the house but
OL,19,Frefused to provide a sample despite
OL,20,Fbeing asked several times.
