OL,7,FTeesside Magistrates' Court heard the
OL,8,Fdefendant, who played cricket for
OL,9,FEngland under-19s and Durham before
OL,10,Fretiring in 2002 to pursue an umpiring
OL,11,Fcareer, did not believe he had to
OL,12,Fprovide a specimen.
OL,14,FHe did however plead guilty and was
OL,15,Fbanned from the roads.
