OL,7,FProsecuting, Olivia Randell, told the
OL,8,Fcourt Gough's partner told police they
OL,9,Fhad been drinking in the city. They
OL,10,Freturned separately with Gough seen on
OL,11,FCCTV driving his own car while his
OL,12,Fpartner caught a taxi.
OL,14,FTom Bennett, mitigating, said police
OL,15,Fhad attended the house on the back of
OL,16,Fconcerns raised by Gough.
OL,18,F"Having spoken to police he went into
OL,19,Fthe house to show police had had
OL,20,Fconsumed some alcohol once he got
OL,21,Fhome," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
