OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FHe said Gough claims he did not drink
OL,8,Fbefore driving but had consumed
OL,9,Falcohol when he got home before police
OL,10,Farrived.
OL,12,F"He didn't believe he had to provide a
OL,13,Fspecimen for those reasons," he said.
OL,15,FGough, of Tulip Close, in the Bishop
OL,16,FCuthbert area of Hartlepool, admitted
OL,17,Ffailing to provide a specimen for
OL,18,Fbreath analysis.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
